---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout 
  title="LICAP - Liver Cancer Awareness Program | SALi"
  description="LICAP (Liver Cancer Awareness Program) at South Asian Liver Institute. Comprehensive liver cancer screening, education, and support for patients and families."
  keywords="LICAP, Liver Cancer Awareness Program, liver cancer screening, HCC awareness, liver cancer support, SALi programmes"
  image="/assets/images/banners/7.jpg"
  type="article"
  section="Patient Programmes"
  tags={["LICAP", "liver cancer", "patient support", "awareness program"]}
>
    <!-- ========================
       page title 
    =========================== -->
    <section class="page-title page-title-layout2 bg-overlay text-center pb-0">
      <div class="bg-img"><img src="/assets/images/page-titles/3.jpg" alt="background"></div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-8 offset-xl-2">
            <div class="pagetitle__icon">
              <i class="icon-microscope"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="pagetitle__heading">LICAP Program</h1>
            <p class="pagetitle__desc mb-30">The Liver Cancer Awareness Program (LICAP) at SALi is dedicated to providing comprehensive care and support for patients with liver cancer. We are committed to raising awareness and improving outcomes through advanced treatment and research.</p>
            <a href="#content" class="scroll-down"><i class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-down"></i></a>
          </div><!-- /.col-xl-8 -->
        </div><!-- /.row -->
      </div><!-- /.container -->
    </section><!-- /.page-title -->

    <section id="content" class=" pb-80">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-8">
            <div class="text-block mb-50">
              <p class="text-block__desc mb-20 font-weight-bold color-secondary">Our multidisciplinary team of experts provides specialized care for liver cancer patients, from diagnosis to treatment and long-term management. We use the latest technologies and evidence-based practices to ensure the best possible outcomes.</p>
              <div class="video-banner-layout3 bg-overlay mb-50">
                <img src="/assets/images/banners/7.jpg" alt="banner">
                <a class="video__btn video__btn-white popup-video" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nrJtHemSPW4">
                  <div class="video__player">
                    <i class="fa fa-play"></i>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div><!-- /.video-banner -->
              <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">The LICAP program is designed to support patients and their families throughout their journey. We offer personalized care plans, educational resources, and access to clinical trials to ensure comprehensive and compassionate care.</p>
            </div><!-- /.text-block -->

            <ul class="list-items list-unstyled mb-60 pl-40">
              <li>Early detection and diagnosis of liver cancer.</li>
              <li>Advanced treatment options, including surgery, chemotherapy, and radiation therapy.</li>
              <li>Supportive care to manage symptoms and improve quality of life.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="widget-plan mb-60">
              <div class="widget__body">
                <h5 class="widget__title">Health Care Plans</h5>
                <p>Our program includes a range of services tailored to meet the individual needs of each patient. We work with you to develop a personalized care plan that addresses your specific condition and supports your overall well-being.
                </p>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                    <div class="plan__items">
                      <ul class="list-items list-items-layout2 list-unstyled mb-0">
                        <li>Comprehensive medical assessments.</li>
                        <li>Personalized treatment plans.</li>
                        <li>Ongoing monitoring and support.</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div><!-- /.col-md-6 -->
                  <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                    <div class="plan__items">
                      <ul class="list-items list-items-layout2 list-unstyled mb-0">
                        <li>Nutritional counseling and support.</li>
                        <li>Access to clinical trials.</li>
                        <li>Patient and family education.</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div><!-- /.col-md-6 -->
                </div><!-- /.row -->
              </div><!-- /.widget__body -->
            </div><!-- /.widget-plan -->
            <div class="text-block mb-50">
              <h5 class="text-block__title">Our Core Values</h5>
              <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">At SALi, we are committed to providing patient-centered care that is compassionate, respectful, and of the highest quality. Our core values guide everything we do, from clinical practice to research and education.</p>
            </div><!-- /.text-block -->
            <div class="fancybox-layout1">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <!-- fancybox item #1 -->
                  <div class="fancybox-item d-flex">
                    <div class="fancybox__icon">
                      <i class="icon-heart"></i>
                    </div><!-- /.fancybox__icon -->
                    <div class="fancybox__content">
                      <h4 class="fancybox__title">Patient-Centered Care</h4>
                      <p class="fancybox__desc">We prioritize the needs and preferences of our patients, ensuring they are active partners in their care.</p>
                    </div><!-- /.fancybox-content -->
                  </div><!-- /.fancybox-item -->
                </div><!-- /.col-md-6 -->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <!-- fancybox item #2 -->
                  <div class="fancybox-item d-flex">
                    <div class="fancybox__icon">
                      <i class="icon-doctor"></i>
                    </div><!-- /.fancybox__icon -->
                    <div class="fancybox__content">
                      <h4 class="fancybox__title">Clinical Excellence</h4>
                      <p class="fancybox__desc">We are dedicated to providing the highest standard of medical care through continuous learning and innovation.</p>
                    </div><!-- /.fancy-content -->
                  </div><!-- /.fancybox-item -->
                </div><!-- /.col-md-6 -->
              </div><!-- /.row -->
            </div><!-- /.fancybox-layout1 -->
            <div class="text-block mb-50">
              <h5 class="text-block__title">Health Tips & Info</h5>
              <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">We are here to answer all of your questions and provide the information you need to make informed decisions about your health. We believe that education is a key component of effective cancer care.</p>
            </div><!-- /.text-block -->
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-8 -->
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4">
            <aside class="sidebar has-marign-left sticky-top">
              <div class="widget widget-services">
                <h5 class="widget__title">Our Programmes</h5>
                <div class="widget-content">
                  <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                    <li><a href="/programmes/licap"><span>LICAP</span><i class="icon-arrow-right"></i></a></li>
                    <li><a href="/programmes/ascites-club"><span>Ascites Club</span><i class="icon-arrow-right"></i></a></li>
                    <li><a href="/programmes/liver-line"><span>Liver Line</span><i class="icon-arrow-right"></i></a></li>
                  </ul>
                </div><!-- /.widget-content -->
              </div><!-- /.widget-services -->
              <div class="widget widget-help bg-overlay bg-overlay-secondary-gradient">
                <div class="bg-img"><img src="/assets/images/banners/5.jpg" alt="background"></div>
                <div class="widget-content">
                  <div class="widget__icon">
                    <i class="icon-call3"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="widget__title">Emergency Cases</h4>
                  <p class="widget__desc">Please feel welcome to contact our friendly reception staff with any general
                    or medical enquiry call us.
                  </p>
                  <a href="tel:+918070670670" class="phone__number">
                    <i class="icon-phone"></i> <span>+91-8070 670 670</span>
                  </a>
                </div><!-- /.widget-content -->
              </div><!-- /.widget-help -->
            </aside><!-- /.sidebar -->
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        </div><!-- /.row -->
      </div><!-- /.container -->
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
